

Summary
This SOP document explains the step wise procedure of troubleshooting for email template issue from keycloak. 
Steps of Procedure:
Checked the both dev and stage environments configurations of keycloak application.
Found the change in Email theme as keycloak in Theme configuration in Stage environment.
Changed the Email Theme as base and saved.
Checked the keycloak deployment configuration file with dev.
Checked the email configuration folder in the keycloak Pod in both dev and stage.
Found wrongly placed email path for template creation. 
Taken the backup from dev and replicated it on stage environment.
Tested the connection.


To resolve the issue we thought to check by changing all the files that act in sending the mail
created all the files in the email directory. (text file has the configuration that integrates to send the templates)
Restarted the keycloak deploy.


